latestPosts.caption:
Switching worlds but keeping the style constant, Crocs for every side of me 🥰

#YourCrocsYourStoryYourWorld #CrocsIndia #ad

A 90 day photo dump - aka a glimpse into the most consistent I’ve ever been.
From 12 - 15k steps a day (even when 10K felt like a stretch), post-meal walks just to feel better and stay moving, home-cooked meals full of veggies, fruits, protein, and carbs and to lifting + mma five days a week AANNNND running 5ks on Sundays when I could 🥵

Some days were easy. Most weren’t. But I showed up anyway.
Even when I didn’t feel like it, I reminded myself : this isn’t about motivation - it’s about discipline. And now, what started as a 90-day challenge feels like second nature.

Physically, I’ve changed. Mentally, even more.
This became more than just fitness - it became therapy, routine, and a reminder that I’m capable of so much more than I give myself credit for

Huge thank you to @onthemove.life @rishonthemove : none of this would’ve happened without you. 
@onepunchmma_ and specially @mitts_and_moves : thank you for helping me level up in EVERY way.

90 days down but baby we still going & still growing 🤪🥰
